Package: siduction-art-kde-desperado
Architecture: all
Provides: siduction-art-kde-theme
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, creativecommons3,
 siduction-art-ksplash-desperado,
 siduction-art-kdm-desperado
Recommends: siduction-art-wallpaper-desperado, dmz-cursor-theme
Description: KDE theme for the siduction 12.1 release
 release specific metapackage depending on ksplash, kdm and KDE themes to be
 used in combination with the K Desktop Environment. This package also
 provides a release specific color scheme for KDE.
 .
 KDE artwork metapackage for: siduction 12.1 (Desperado)

Package: siduction-art-kdm-desperado
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, creativecommons3, kdm
Description: KDM theme for the siduction 12.1 release
 release specific artwork theme for the KDM display manager to be used in
 combination with the K Desktop Environment.
 .
 KDM artwork for: siduction 12.1 (Desperado)
 .
 This package does not override existing theme configurations and needs to be
 selected manually.

Package: siduction-art-ksplash-desperado
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, creativecommons3, kdebase-workspace-bin
Description: KDE ksplash theme for the siduction 12.1 release
 release specific KDE ksplash theme, using the default ksplash engine.
 .
 KDE ksplash artwork for: siduction 12.1 (Desperado)
 .
 This package does not override existing theme configurations and needs to be
 selected manually.

Package: siduction-art-wallpaper-desperado
Architecture: all
Provides: siduction-art-wallpaper-theme
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, creativecommons3
Description: siduction wallpaper for the 12.1 release
 release specific wallpapers, compatible with the K Desktop Environment, Xfce,
 LXDE and GNOME.
 .
 Wallpapers for: siduction 12.1 (Desperado)
 .
 This package does not override existing theme configurations and needs to be
 selected manually.

Package: siduction-art-xfce-desperado
Architecture: all
Provides: siduction-art-xfce-theme
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, creativecommons3, siduction-art-xsplash-desperado
Recommends: siduction-art-wallpaper-desperado,  dmz-cursor-theme
Description: Xfce theme for the siduction 12.1 release
 release specific metapackage depending on xfce4-session, gdm3 and Xfce themes
 to be used in combination with the Xfce desktop environment.
 .
 Xfce artwork metapackage for: siduction 12.1 (Desperado)

Package: siduction-art-xsplash-desperado
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, creativecommons3, xfce4-session
Description: Xfce splash theme for the siduction 12.1 release
 release specific Xfce splash theme, based on the balou theme engine.
 .
 Xfce xsplash artwork for: sidcution 12.1 (Desperado)
 .
 This package does not override existing theme configurations and needs to be
 selected manually.

